<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<title>${persona_name} — feed that would have been (${run_date})</title>
<style>
  :root { color-scheme: dark; }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; }
  body {
    margin: 0; padding: 2rem 1rem;
    background: #191b22; color: #e6e9ef;
    font: 16px/1.5 -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, sans-serif;
  }
  .column { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .profile {
    background: #282c37; border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.25rem;
    display: flex; gap: 1rem; align-items: flex-start; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .avatar {
    width: 56px; height: 56px; border-radius: 50%; flex: none;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6364ff, #79bd9a);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 28px;
  }
  .profile h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 1.1rem; }
  .handle { color: #9aa0b5; font-size: .9rem; }
  .bio { margin: .4rem 0 0; font-size: .9rem; color: #c3c8d4; }
  .runline { margin: .5rem 0 0; font-size: .8rem; color: #9aa0b5; }
  .runline code { color: #79bd9a; }
  .banner {
    background: #3a2f15; border: 1px solid #8a6d1d; border-radius: 8px;
    padding: .6rem .9rem; font-size: .85rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: #ffd97a;
  }
  .card {
    background: #282c37; border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.1rem 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .card.empty { color: #9aa0b5; font-style: italic; }
  .meta { display: flex; gap: .75rem; align-items: center; font-size: .75rem; color: #9aa0b5; margin-bottom: .6rem; }
  .badge { border-radius: 999px; padding: .1rem .6rem; font-weight: 600; }
  .badge.ok { background: #1f3d2b; color: #79bd9a; }
  .badge.over { background: #4a1f24; color: #ff7a85; }
  .engine { background: #1f2330; border-radius: 999px; padding: .1rem .6rem; }
  .text { white-space: normal; overflow-wrap: anywhere; }
  .text a, .source a { color: #8c8dff; }
  .change-strip {
    margin-top: .8rem; padding: .6rem .8rem; font-size: .85rem;
    background: #20283b; border-left: 3px solid #6364ff; border-radius: 6px;
  }
  .old { color: #ff9aa2; text-decoration: line-through; }
  .new { color: #79bd9a; }
  .why { color: #9aa0b5; }
  .source { margin-top: .8rem; font-size: .8rem; color: #9aa0b5; overflow-wrap: anywhere; }
  .footer {
    background: #20232e; border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.1rem 1.25rem;
    margin-top: 2rem; font-size: .9rem;
  }
  .footer h2 { font-size: 1rem; margin: 0 0 .5rem; }
  .footer h2:not(:first-child) { margin-top: 1.2rem; }
  .footer ul { margin: .3rem 0; padding-left: 1.2rem; }
  .footer li { margin-bottom: .35rem; }
  code { background: #1f2330; padding: .05rem .35rem; border-radius: 4px; font-size: .85em; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="column">
  <div class="profile">
    <div class="avatar">🔌</div>
    <div>
      <h1>${persona_name} <span class="handle">${persona_handle}</span></h1>
      <p class="bio">${persona_bio}</p>
      <p class="runline">run <code>${run_date}</code> · engine <code>${engine}</code> · ${stats}</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="banner">⚠️ Simulation — nothing here was posted anywhere. This is the feed that <em>would have been</em>.</div>
  ${cards}
  <div class="footer">
    <h2>Opinion changes this run</h2>
    ${changes_html}
    <h2>Diary</h2>
    ${diary_html}
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
